  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there-- Poland send out a lot of pants for export to the Belgian Congo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So this was a big industry, and the whole industry is in small homes, and poor homes, like to say, where they're working day and night to make a living.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was there, what to bring them to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was very young in that time, very energetic and strong.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And believe in-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I believe in something I will do for my family, and this holds me very strong and very healthy to be in a family.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In general, my mind is a very family mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I like the family together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we're working all together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, well, I belonged to different organizations, you know, like the young-- and the pogroms in Poland, the [NON-ENGLISH], the big pogrom against Jews, in the false propaganda of the communist.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It make me look-- make me dream of something on the other side from the border, where there is a better life for Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But after being there, I find out communism and fascism and Nazism, there is more-- there is-- they have more in common, like with the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I learned in a hard way being in Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I would have to say the truth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very interested, because you don't-- pogrom their anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And where you're going, in their sole propaganda there, we feel it like we believe it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we believe it not because we believe it-- we wanted to believe it's true, because I have got no choice.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The discrimination against Jews and the anti-Semitism is so big, and we believe that there is a paradise, and we didn't realize how Stalin and Hitler, they have a common goal against the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
